---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Samaya from "../assets/samaya.jpg";
import Book2 from "../components/Book2.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Placeholder Bio Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-col-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:text-left mb-12">
      <div class="xl:col-span-4 grid mt-6">
        <div
          class="w-64 h-64 lg:w-96 lg:h-96 rounded-full justify-self-center bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-32 h-32 text-gray-400"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="xl:col-span-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Maria Mitchell
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">LAc, MTCM</p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do
          eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad
          minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
          aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum
          dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non
          proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est
          laborum.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem
          accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae
          ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta
          sunt explicabo.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <hr class="border-gray-200 my-12" />

    <!-- Samaya's Bio Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-col-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:text-left">
      <div class="xl:col-span-4 grid mt-6">
        <Image
          src={Samaya}
          alt="Samaya Cullerton"
          class="w-64 h-64 lg:w-96 lg:h-96 rounded-full justify-self-center"
          width={384}
          height={384}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="xl:col-span-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Samaya Cullerton
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">
          LAc, MTCM Traditional Family Medicine
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          Samaya Cullerton, L.Ac., is a licensed acupuncturist and herbalist who
          brings warmth, deep knowledge, and over a decade of clinical
          experience to her work at Wellness Medical Center. With a Master’s
          Degree in Traditional Chinese Medicine, she specializes in women’s
          health, fertility, prenatal and postpartum care, and pediatric support
          — all approached through a holistic, evidence-informed lens. As part
          of the clinic’s collaborative team, Samaya offers integrative care
          that honors each patient’s unique needs and life stage.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          Outside of the clinic, Samaya is also a professor in the doctoral
          program at Five Branches University, where she teaches herbal
          medicine, dietetics, and clinical acupuncture. She maintains a private
          practice as well, which you can learn more about at
          <a
            href="https://www.samayacullerton.com"
            class="text-[#bf7644] hover:text-orange-800">samayacullerton.com</a
          >.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
          I am in the Central California Alliance for Health Insurance provider
          network and I am currently accepting new patients.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 items-center">
          <Book2 />
          <img
            src="/AllianceLogo.svg"
            alt="Central California Alliance for Health Insurance logo"
            class="w-16 h-16 justify-self-center md:justify-self-end"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
